title: S14 Ep61: Remembering Rosemary Ellen Guiley
itunes:title: Remembering Rosemary Ellen Guiley
description:
Prolific paranormal author and friend of BEYOND the DARKNESS, Rosemary Ellen Guiley has passed away at the age of 69...

Rosemary was a cornerstone in the launch of both Darkness Radio and Darkness Events and we wanted to take today to honor her memory by presenting her very first appearance with us in January of 2006 and her last appearance with us in May of 2018.

Rosemary was still producing projects of her own and with other people through her own imprint, Visionary Living up until her passing. You can check out her catalog at https://visionarylivingpublishing.com/
